snippet: Fourteen-times grand slam champion Rafa Nadal has turned to fellow Mallorcan Carlos Moya in an attempt to revitalize his career, the 30-year-old Spaniard said on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Fourteen-times grand slam champion Rafa Nadal has turned to fellow Mallorcan Carlos Moya in an attempt to revitalize his career, the 30-year-old Spaniard said on Saturday.

headline.main: Carlos Moya Joins Nadal's Coaching Team
headline.print_headline: Carlos Moya Joins Nadal's Coaching Team
